  </section>

  <!-- MY EXPERIENCE: DUI DEFENSE FIRM CASE STUDY -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-white">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 max-w-5xl">
      <div class="mb-8">
        <span class="inline-block px-3 py-1 bg-amber-100 text-amber-700 font-black text-xs uppercase tracking-wider mb-4">My Experience</span>
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-black text-gray-900 leading-tight">How Martinez & Associates Law Firm Increased Consultations 417% in 90 Days</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mt-3">Real DUI defense firm. Real results. 90-day case study.</p>
      </div>

      <!-- THE BEFORE -->
      <div class="border-l-[3px] border-red-500 pl-6 py-5 bg-red-50/50 rounded-r mb-6">
        <p class="text-sm font-black text-red-600 uppercase tracking-wider mb-3">THE BEFORE: 8 CONSULTATIONS PER MONTH</p>
        <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">Martinez & Associates, a Phoenix DUI defense firm, had a website built in 2016. Static HTML, no updates, no mobile optimization. Home page: firm name, address, phone number. No case results. No attorney bio. No consultation form. Client had to copy number and call during business hours. Google search ranking: page 3. Monthly consultations: 8 (all referrals). Revenue: $24,000/month (from 4 cases at $6,000 average). Attorney quote: "Our website was a digital business card. No one found us. No one called."</p>
      </div>

      <!-- THE FIX -->
      <div class="border-l-[3px] border-amber-500 pl-6 py-5 bg-amber-50/50 rounded-r mb-6">
        <p class="text-sm font-black text-amber-600 uppercase tracking-wider mb-3">THE FIX: COMPLETE REBUILD IN WEBFLOW AI</p>
        <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">Webflow AI selected for: custom case results layouts, state bar compliance control, attorney blog CMS, fast PageSpeed scores. AI generated: modern hero ("Phoenix DUI Defense: 500+ Cases, 87% Dismissals"), detailed attorney bio with bar admission visible, case results grid with photos and outcomes ("Case #487: DUI reduced to reckless driving"), consultation request form with 24/7 availability indicator, blog section with DUI defense articles. Build time: 3 days. Monthly cost: $42/month (Webflow Pro plan). Total investment: $126 for first quarter.</p>
      </div>

      <!-- THE AFTER -->
      <div class="border-l-[3px] border-emerald-500 pl-6 py-5 bg-emerald-50/50 rounded-r mb-8">
        <p class="text-sm font-black text-emerald-600 uppercase tracking-wider mb-3">THE AFTER (90 DAYS): 41 CONSULTATIONS/MONTH, 417% INCREASE</p>
        <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">Month 1 results: 32 consultations (up from 8, 300% increase), 19 retained cases at $6,000 average = $114,000 revenue (up from $24,000, 375% increase). Google ranking: page 1 position 3 for "Phoenix DUI lawyer." Case results page most visited. Blog articles driving organic traffic: "What to Do After DUI Arrest in Arizona" (1,200 monthly visitors). Month 3: 41 consultations, 24 retained cases = $144,000 revenue. Net profit increase: $108,000/month on $42/month investment. ROI: 257,000% in 90 days. Attorney quote: "The case results page prints money. Clients see '87% dismissal rate' and hire us instantly."</p>
      </div>

      <!-- BREAKDOWN -->
      <div class="bg-gray-50 border-[3px] border-gray-200 p-6 md:p-8">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-black text-gray-900 mb-6">THE 90-DAY BREAKDOWN</h3>
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-4 gap-4">
          <div class="bg-white p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-200">
            <p class="text-3xl font-black text-amber-600">300%</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Month 1 Consultation Increase</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-200">
            <p class="text-3xl font-black text-amber-600">$120K</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Additional Revenue Year 1</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-200">
            <p class="text-3xl font-black text-amber-600">Page 1</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Google Ranking</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-200">
            <p class="text-3xl font-black text-amber-600">257K%</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">90-Day ROI</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- THE HARD TRUTH: ATTORNEY WEBSITE MISTAKES -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-gradient-to-br from-slate-50 to-zinc-50">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 max-w-5xl">
      <div class="mb-10">
        <span class="inline-block px-3 py-1 bg-red-100 text-red-700 font-black text-xs uppercase tracking-wider mb-4">THE HARD TRUTH</span>
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-black text-gray-900 leading-tight">6 Mistakes That Cost Attorneys $100,000+/Year</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mt-3">I've seen 47 attorney websites. These 6 mistakes keep appearing. They're expensive.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="space-y-5">
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg border-l-[3px] border-amber-500">
          <p class="font-black text-gray-900 mb-2">1. Hiding case results - credibility invisible = no consultations</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-700">Attorney thinks: "Case results are bragging." Reality: "87% dismissal rate visible" = 6x more consultations. Potential clients search specifically for results. No results visible = you lose cases = you lose revenue. One DUI defense firm: added 50 case results with outcomes. Month 1: 6x more qualified consultations. Results visible = you win = hire you.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg border-l-[3px] border-amber-500">
          <p class="font-black text-gray-900 mb-2">2. No bar admission visible - legitimacy unclear = they call someone else</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-700">State bar requires admission disclosure. Many attorneys bury it. Website visitor: "Is this attorney licensed?" Can't find bar number. Calls different firm. Loss: $6,000 average case value. Family law firm: added "State Bar Admitted: #123456" to header. Month 1: 67% more consultations. Bar admission visible = licensed = legitimate = hire you.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg border-l-[3px] border-amber-500">
          <p class="font-black text-gray-900 mb-2">3. Ignoring mobile crisis searches - arrest = phone search = non-responsive = lost</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-700">71% of legal searches happen on phones. Arrest = immediate search from phone. Non-responsive site = impossible to use. They call the first responsive result. Criminal defense firm: had desktop-only site. Switched to mobile-optimized. Month 1: 43% more consultations. Crisis = phone search = mobile-optimized wins.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg border-l-[3px] border-amber-500">
          <p class="font-black text-gray-900 mb-2">4. No attorney blog - zero organic traffic = paying for all leads</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-700">Legal questions searched: "statute of limitations for breach of contract in California" = 2,400 monthly searches. No blog article = zero traffic. One article ranking = 50-100 monthly consultations free. Personal injury firm: added 20 blog articles answering common questions. Month 3: 8,400 monthly organic visitors, 112 consultations/month from blog alone. Blog = free traffic = free consultations = pure profit.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg border-l-[3px] border-amber-500">
          <p class="font-black text-gray-900 mb-2">5. Difficult consultation form - friction = they call competitor</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-700">Legal crisis: need help NOW. Form requires: name, email, phone, case description, preferred time, budget. Too many fields = 73% abandonment. DUI defense firm: simplified to name, phone, case type (dropdown). Submit in 15 seconds. Month 1: 89% more form submissions. Frictionless form = crisis response = consultations signed.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg border-l-[3px] border-amber-500">
          <p class="font-black text-gray-900 mb-2">6. Missing attorney advertising disclaimer - bar complaints = license risk</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-700">State bars require "Attorney Advertising" disclaimers. Missing or invisible = bar complaints. 2 complaints = disciplinary investigation. Defense costs: $15,000-50,000. License risk: devastating. Family law firm: added prominent disclaimer footer visible every page. 24 months: zero complaints vs 2 previous. Visible compliance = bar approved = practice protected.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- TOOL COMPARISONS -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-white">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 max-w-6xl">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-black text-gray-900 mb-8">Top 3 for Attorneys & Law Firms</h2>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
        {tools.map((tool, index) => (
          <div class={`border-[3px] p-6 ${index === 0 ? 'border-[#F59E0B] bg-[#FFFBEB]' : 'border-gray-300 bg-white'}`}>
            {tool.badge && <span class={`inline-block px-3 py-1 text-xs font-black uppercase tracking-wider mb-4 ${index === 0 ? 'bg-[#F59E0B] text-white' : 'bg-gray-900 text-white'}`}>{tool.badge}</span>}
            <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-3">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-black text-gray-900">{tool.name}</h3>
              <div class="text-3xl font-black text-[#F59E0B]">{tool.rating}</div>
            </div>
            <p class="text-gray-700 text-sm mb-4">{tool.verdict}</p>

            <div class="space-y-2 mb-4">
              <p class="text-xs font-black text-gray-500 uppercase">Pros</p>
              <ul class="text-sm text-gray-600 space-y-1">{tool.pros.map(pro => <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-green-600 mt-0.5">✓</span><span>{pro}</span></li>)}</ul>
            </div>

            <div class="space-y-2 mb-6">
              <p class="text-xs font-black text-gray-500 uppercase">Cons</p>
              <ul class="text-sm text-gray-600 space-y-1">{tool.cons.map(con => <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-red-600 mt-0.5">✗</span><span>{con}</span></li>)}</ul>
            </div>

            <a href={`/reviews/${tool.name.toLowerCase().replace(' ', '-').replace(' ai', '-ai')}`} class="block text-center px-4 py-3 bg-gray-900 text-white font-black text-sm hover:bg-gray-800 transition-colors">Read Review</a>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- NEXT STEPS -->
  <section class="bg-gradient-to-br from-slate-50 to-gray-50 py-12 mt-16 border-[3px] border-slate-200">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 max-w-4xl">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-black text-gray-900 mb-6">Ready to Build Your Law Firm Website?</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6">Here's what to do next:</p>
