            <p class="text-sm text-gray-700">Custom case results layouts: full-width images with outcomes, charges filed, dismissal rates visible. Attorney bio with bar admission prominently displayed. Attorney blog CMS for DUI defense articles driving organic traffic. Fast PageSpeed scores (95+) for mobile crisis searches. Code export for custom appointment scheduling integrations.</p>
